Output assets/demo.gif
Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1000
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 20ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 2

Type `claude -p "Create an app icon from ~/Desktop/logo.svg with a dark blue (#1C1C2E) background at 250% scale, then render a Liquid Glass preview on the sine-magenta background to ~/Desktop/icon-preview.png" --allowedTools "mcp__icon-composer__create_icon,mcp__icon-composer__export_preview,mcp__icon-composer__render_liquid_glass,mcp__icon-composer__set_layer_position"`
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 180s
